&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="notice-body">&lt;p>如果你在iCloud中按照上一节的步骤购买了域名，可以跳过本节。&lt;/p>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>在&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.icloud.com/icloudplus/customdomain" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
